n Friends of the Louvre en 2014.","placeOfCreation":"","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Victoire Boze, fille de l\u0027artiste ; don au Louvre en 1866. Expos\u00e9 au Salon de la Correspondance de 1782 (nov.) puis \u00e0 celui de 1783 (f\u00e9v.) et au Salon de 1791. Rest\u00e9 en possession de l\u0027artiste, puis de son avant-derni\u00e8re fille Victoire Ursule Madeleine (1785-1871), qui en fit don au mus\u00e9e du Louvre en 1866 (A.L., D 8 1866, 14 mai : lettre de Victoire Boze et remerciements du directeur le 24 mai). Restaur\u00e9 en 2012 (d\u00e9poussi\u00e9rage de la toile de marouflage, consolidation des d\u00e9chirures sur les bords et le papier de bordage).","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Derni\u00e8re provenance : Boze, Victoire Ursule M.","note":""}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"don","doubt":"","dates":[{"startYear":1866,"endYear":null}]}],"ownedBy":"","heldBy":"","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"collection":[{"value":"Boze, Joseph"},{"value":"Boze, Victoire"}],"person":[{"value":"Boze, Joseph"}],"subject":[{"value":"Autoportrait"},{"value":"Salon de la Correspondance de 1782"},{"value":"Salon de la Correspondance de 1783"},{"value":"Salon de 1791"}],"technic":[{"value":"papier bleu"},{"value":"pastel"}]},"bibliography":[],"exhibition":[],"relatedWork":[],"image":[{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/original\/11\/14\/49\/00\/AGO111449-000_PE.jpg","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/small\/11\/14\/49\/00\/AGO111449-000_PE.jpg","copyright":"GrandPalaisRmn (Mus\u00e9e du Louvre) \/ Tony Querrec","type":"","position":0},{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/original\/11\/14\/49\/00\/AGO111449-001_PE.jpg","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/small\/11\/14\/49\/00\/AGO111449-001_PE.jpg","copyright":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, dist. GrandPalaisRmn \/ Martine Beck-Co